OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBBC stuck in TV era without
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdigital plan, MPs say      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The BBC is stuck in a "yesteryear" of  
OL,6, TV and radio without a plan for        
OL,7, delivering its services in a digital   
OL,8, future, according to a report by MPs.  
OL,10,FHowever, the Public Accounts Committee 
OL,11,Falso cautioned against the corporation 
OL,12,Fmoving too quickly towards             
OL,13,Finternet-only broadcasting.            
OL,15,FIt warned against excluding those who  
OL,16,Fcannot access digital services due to a
OL,17,Flack of broadband coverage.            
OL,19,FBBC director general Tim Davie expects 
OL,20,Fa switchover to digital from the 2030s.
